OL,3,C'Extraordinary' increase in abuse
OL,4,Caimed at GP staff, top medic warns
OL,6,FMore than a quarter (28%) said they or
OL,7,Ftheir team had been the victim of
OL,8,Fphysical violence from patients, while
OL,9,Fmore than a third (35%) said they had
OL,10,Fsuffered racial abuse and 15% told the
OL,11,Fpoll they had been the victim of
OL,12,Fsexual abuse.
